</svg></div><div class="o-container"><div class="o-row"><div fade="" class="o-col _w-12 sm-w-24"><h2 class="t-display-3">Our path to wireless power you can depend on</h2></div></div><div class="o-row about margin-24"><div fade="" class="o-col _w-8 sm-w-24"><p class="t-body-2">Aaron, Phyo, Grayson, and Charlie were brought together by a passion for power electronics and a desire to make the world a better place, first overlapping at a conference in Italy.<br/><br/>On the conference floor, they dreamed of how high-frequency power electronics and incredible electromagnetics could transform wireless power and accelerate electrification.<br/><br/>A few months later, Resonant Link was launched around a revolutionary way to send wireless power that was 5x faster than anything else available then — or since.</p></div><div class="o-col _w-16 shrink-0 sm-w-24"><div image-reveal="" parallax="" class="c-img-contain team"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6356a48dff70251d68facdf8/639c499bb7572c329c6def56_team.webp" loading="lazy" alt="" class="c-img"/></div></div></div><div class="o-row content-end margin-312"><div fade="" class="o-col _w-16 sm-w-24"><h2 class="t-display-4 indent-32">Our founding team was laser-focused on using wireless charging to speed the adoption of electric vehicles and address the coming global health crisis of climate change.</h2></div></div><div class="o-row ab-tech margin-176"><div class="o-col _w-12 hide-tablet"></div><div class="c-img-contain ab-tech"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6356a48dff70251d68facdf8/63989f5bdb675b3528d7f095_ab-resonant.webp" loading="eager" alt="" class="c-img ab-tech"/></div><div class="o-col _w-9 md-w-16 sm-w-24 z-index-1"><div fade="" class="margin-56"><p class="t-body-2 is-grey100">They also realized that wireless charging could save lives right away by eliminating the wires and battery replacement surgeries needed to power implanted medical devices, like pacemakers.<br/><br/>Less than a year after forming, Resonant Link partnered with their first Fortune 500 customer, who had been working on wireless power for half a century, to develop non-invasive wireless power for a life-saving medical device. With this first success, Resonant Link started on the path to center electricity for human health, inside and out.<br/><br/>Today, the Resonant Link team delivers 5x faster and highly-efficient wireless power for applications big to small, from massive industrial trucks to medical devices smaller than a fingernail.<br/><br/>Resonant Link is anchored by offices in South Burlington, VT, Zurich, CH, and Boston, MA, and has amassed double-digit customers in healthcare, electric vehicles, and consumer electronics.<br/><br/>With backing from top investors and government agencies, they are poised to continue their exponential growth and lead the movement to electrify work, logistics, transportation, and patient care to help people, businesses, and the planet thrive.</p></div><div fade="" class="o-col _w-14 sm-w-20"><a id="w-node-_060fbb9c-011c-33d0-6735-e7a308e3a0e8-08e3a0e8" href="/contact" class="c-btn is-main w-inline-block"><div class="c-btn-inner is-main"><div class="c-btn-txt"><p class="t-label-4 is-1">Let’s talk</p><p no-click="" class="t-label-4 is-2"> </p></div><div class="c-btn-icon w-embed"><svg width="1.5em" height="1.5em" viewBox="0 0 25 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
